OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774469469
OL,3,CDriving licence lost on beach reunited
OL,4,Cwith owner after more than 25 years
OL,6,FA man has described the surprise of
OL,7,Fbeing reunited with his provisional
OL,8,Fdriving licence, which washed up on a
OL,9,Fbeach in Cornwall after more than 25
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FThe provisional licence, believed to
OL,13,Fhave been lost in the 2000s, was found
OL,14,Fby Christopher Chard while walking
OL,15,Falong Great Western Beach, in Newquay,
OL,16,Fon Saturday 21 March.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
