PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774469469
OL,3,CDriving licence lost on beach reunited
OL,4,Cwith owner after more than 25 years
OL,6,FMore than 25 years on, he managed to
OL,7,Ftrack down the owner, Kevin Stark,
OL,8,Fafter posting an image on social media
OL,9,Fand said he hoped he had passed his
OL,10,Ftest after all these years.
OL,12,FIn a post on Facebook, Mr Chard said:
OL,13,F"Found this provisional licence on
OL,14,FGreat Western. I hope you have been
OL,15,Fable to pass your test after all these
OL,16,Fyears. Newquay address. Lost in the
OL,17,F2000s is my prediction."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
