FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774469469
OL,3,CDriving licence lost on beach reunited
OL,4,Cwith owner after more than 25 years
OL,6,FMr Stark said being reunited with the
OL,7,Fold provisional driving licence was
OL,8,F"like someone had rewound the last 26
OL,9,Fyears," adding, "life is full of
OL,10,Fsurprises."
OL,12,FAged 17 at the time it was lost, Mr
OL,13,FStark confirmed he passed his test
OL,14,F"probably not long after that" and was
OL,15,Fdriving around the streets of Newquay,
OL,16,F"thinking I was something special no
OL,17,Fdoubt!"
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
