FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774469469
OL,3,CDriving licence lost on beach reunited
OL,4,Cwith owner after more than 25 years
OL,6,FNow living on the Isle of Man with his
OL,7,Ffour children, he said a lot has
OL,8,Fchanged since then, and that he will
OL,9,Fno doubt be sorting out their
OL,10,Fprovisional licences soon.
OL,12,FThe quarter-of-a-century-old photocard
OL,13,Fis one of many things that have washed
OL,14,Fup on Cornish beaches, including rare
OL,15,FLego pieces, a teddy bear in need of
OL,16,Frestoration and a package containing
OL,17,F#100k of cocaine.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
